Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.56,0:01:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair和Lumiere？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.76,0:01:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在ES成员中除名了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.06,0:01:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.96,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是2056454
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.06,0:01:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOTT驱逐舰Preamps和LSU Canopus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.36,0:01:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急情况 我们要求立刻进入直线跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.96,0:02:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 这里是控制台 请进入跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过 Preamps和LSU Canopus
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况变得很糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.36,0:02:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须闯过这关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.66,0:02:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 这是我们的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一个男孩对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 下个月就5岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就应该对他进行教育了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.26,0:02:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他无论如何也不要到GOTT任职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.86,0:02:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也要我能活着回去后再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.36,0:02:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射后2分15秒进入亚空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.86,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登记被注销
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.96,0:02:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 被整肃了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.66,0:02:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十二话 死生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.86,0:02:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5分24秒后我们将进入Zero星系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果顺利 我们也许可以躲过总部的搜索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.46,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且藏到某个殖民地去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的一个是LAV-78
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去这里没什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移民率87%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治立场中立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.06,0:03:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也比较容易获得港口停靠许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这样不就成了逃亡者了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法啊 事实正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.66,0:03:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登记被注销
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.06,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是宇宙行星联合政府当局的正式通知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.96,0:03:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须对你下这个命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.76,0:03:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.46,0:03:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.56,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局长已经对我们下达了整肃令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.46,0:03:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.56,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司与部下之间的信赖关系已经完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生漫长 会发生很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是像你们俩 有漫长的人生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.06,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是自己想活这么长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太在意她们俩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.66,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是这样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.46,0:04:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tweedledum
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是贪婪的 因此才是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这是很有趣的说法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.86,0:04:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都曾经做过永生之梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当他们得到了永生时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.06,0:04:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们却说自己并不想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.26,0:04:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是如此 置身事外 当第三者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是监察官 这是我的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.36,0:04:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想开枪打我 请便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不会佩服你这种浪费子弹的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.36,0:04:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是由官方渠道发布的整肃令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.76,0:05:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SO成员一队或二队肯定会追击我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.16,0:05:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据目前的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内务13课可能已经完成了部署
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内务第13课？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 也就是所谓的GOTT整肃部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.36,0:05:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来\N我们差不多该决定吃下一顿晚餐的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们真的想活下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也该进行补给了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.86,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是这么认为的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她们觉得自己能逃掉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们就会试试看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.76,0:05:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她们感到有点同情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不这么想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是对追她们的人更感到同情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错的Earl Gray啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香气适宜 不会妨碍品尝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.36,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我为那两人特地买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过她们两个回来后请她们喝的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间长了味道就淡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.16,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏扫帚只能增添垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具没用了就应该丢掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.86,0:06:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个被丢弃的工具可能就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细检查别出错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微小的错误可能会导致丧命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长有话要说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次作战的目标是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ES成员Eclair和Lumiere
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.96,0:07:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过本队仅限于\N镇压危险分子时才准予战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是将用谈判的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.56,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次任务不是以整肃行动为优先吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会使你们全员平安的回到Aineias
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.66,0:07:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有责任由身为队长的我来承担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.26,0:07:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精力在紧盯目标上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.16,0:07:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要有任何轻率的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.06,0:07:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判的铁则就是耐心交涉以求和解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.36,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对长…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.66,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无权去破坏一个5岁男孩的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.36,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个月才5岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 立刻进入战斗状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分钟后亚空间脱出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.66,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.16,0:08:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 算了 至少补给食物吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说他说得那么难听 他太可怜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只不过是履行监察官的职责罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.96,0:08:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 没有好茶招待…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来点葡萄酒如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 这个很好喝 谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.86,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一见他就有气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.96,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这里悠闲的时候 他还在工作喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.66,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该稍微感谢他才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.76,0:08:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.66,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该把怒气发泄在贵族身上\N而不是他和局长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.56,0:08:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.06,0:09:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没办法像你那样想得开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？被整肃？她们俩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.16,0:09:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太蠢了 小Ec真是个处事笨拙的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.56,0:09:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这盘通心粉是不是咖喱放多了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经抵达LAV-78
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前时间1346
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本局应该已经通知过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关闭认证信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.26,0:09:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从标准降落场西北方进入通用码头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.06,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从西北方的通用码头进入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.06,0:09:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说起来…竟然下整肃命令啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.36,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 我们获准使用D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是内务13课的人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.86,0:10:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是内务13课的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你不会让我们轻松地逃走了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.86,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在程序上 我们必须确认你们的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以选择投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由询问会来决定是非对错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问那个的话 我们的回答是NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.46,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然连你们都派来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在询问会上胜算很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.06,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你们好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么不攻击我们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.96,0:11:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是综合战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.26,0:11:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内务13课只是用来牵制我们的先头部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.06,0:11:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能是在等第一或第二小队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常上下关系分得那么清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.06,0:11:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候反而团结起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.56,0:11:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那说明他们是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.86,0:11:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她自己抹去了记忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还是在重复相同的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.86,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使过了1000年 华尔兹还是华尔兹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种旋律没有变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.36,0:12:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我已经补给完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要离开了 快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.96,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们俩的样子 他们应该已经到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得没错 赶快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.26,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊小队 到前排！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.06,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员瞄准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第二小队的SO成员劳拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.96,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间1643 根据总部的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你们开始实行逮捕程序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗对双方都不好 请你们投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.16,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我拒绝呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在重申一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.76,0:13:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.96,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊小队 启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.96,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见 那可不是普通的拘束线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.06,0:13:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经启动了连接处的起爆装置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.36,0:13:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们反抗 连接处就会分开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.16,0:13:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部的生化雷管会反应并爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样大小的殖民星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概会被炸掉一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太胡闹了 如果那样的话 你们也会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.76,0:13:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所以我们才请你们投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们的生命掌握在你们两个手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们会有一段时间\N不能吃这里的料理了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.86,0:14:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们会变得很忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.56,0:14:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair会求饶吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 怎么可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.36,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在将部下的性命置于危险之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.46,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不公平的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.26,0:14:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也是一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你们逃跑时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.96,0:14:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们挟持了宇宙行星联盟的监察官作为人质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.86,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你们的罪状之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.26,0:14:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.66,0:14:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你把我们的位置通知了他们？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.16,0:14:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是贪婪的 因此才是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这是很有趣的说法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想开枪打我 请便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不会佩服你这种浪费子弹的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 辛苦您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不希望你们死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我们还是决绝呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在任何情况都有办法存活下来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.66,0:15:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那时 很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.46,0:15:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能启动D指令了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.36,0:15:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D指令在未启动前 没有对付的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 能来得及吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.76,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.06,0:15:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.56,0:15:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘束线被无效化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.26,0:15:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤索夫 启动D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和我们的约定不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.66,0:16:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 谈判破裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤索夫 启动D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.06,0:16:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 特殊小队 启动D指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备点火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请输入数字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.46,0:16:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.56,0:16:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23620679
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D指令启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.66,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D指令是使它们体内的纳米细胞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.26,0:16:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是纳米机械 强制膨胀的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.46,0:17:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lumiere…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.66,0:17:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩张的细胞会压迫内部器官直至摧毁它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道哪些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此你为什么还有启动它？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是我们的工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保卫组织 必须有人去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.06,0:17:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做了肮脏的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且通过做这样的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.46,0:17:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的家人才可以\N每年平安的庆祝他们的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.46,0:17:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Mist…疫苗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须使它发挥抗体的效用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 来不及了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他们已经活了很长的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们仍然很年轻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.06,0:18:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没有毁掉她们未来的权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.26,0:18:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙行星联盟的ES成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在注入抗体吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.36,0:19:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经暂时停止了她内部的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.76,0:19:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他的全部记忆会因此而被唤醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能会很残酷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也比死掉要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都曾经做过永生之梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.66,0:19:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但问题在于怎样渡过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.06,0:19:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair 现在传送抗体给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.36,0:19:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是贪婪的 因此才是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不要太过于勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.66,0:19:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受它们原有的样子就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到现在为止的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及从现在开始的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.66,0:20:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说了很难懂得事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题的 否则我也就不会救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.86,0:20:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有句话不是这么说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.96,0:20:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在欺骗敌人之前 必会先骗过盟友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过遗憾的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.16,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是不要和你们俩一起比较好
